des: "Creamy Burrata cheese, sun-dried tomatoes, Kalamata olives, and Italian seasoning combine perfectly to make this delicious hummus! Garnish with fresh basil or parsley."
ins: Combine garbanzo beans, Burrata cheese, olive oil, tahini, Kalamata olives, sun-dried tomatoes, Italian seasoning, and lemon juice in a blender. Blend until smooth, stopping occasionally to scrape down sides.
